Package io.github.kale_ko.bjsl.parsers

Class Parser<T extends com.fasterxml.jackson.core.TokenStreamFactory,V extends com.fasterxml.jackson.core.ObjectCodec>

java.lang.Object
io.github.kale_ko.bjsl.parsers.Parser<T,V>
Type Parameters:
T - The type of the factory used for converting to/from trees/strings
V - The type of the codec used for converting to/from trees/strings
Direct Known Subclasses:
JsonParser, PropertiesParser, SmileParser, TomlParser, XmlParser, YamlParser
public abstract class Parser<T extends com.fasterxml.jackson.core.TokenStreamFactory,V extends com.fasterxml.jackson.core.ObjectCodec> extends Object
An abstract class that all parsers extend from

Contains all the logic for parsing, factories are just passed for values

Basically just a wrapper for Jackson parsers

Since:
1.0.0
